NO WARRANTY.

To install, edit the Makefile as required (default is to use the gcc
compiler, which is assumed to be in your search path), then make.

If desired, move the exectuable and man page to suitable locations.

Questions?  Ask zoe at astro.umd.edu or see the Icarus article!

